## Shopify Editing Patterns

- Use schema-driven development for sections
- Prefer blocks over hardcoded UI
- Keep settings flexible for merchants
- Avoid inline styles unless necessary
- Use Liquid conditionals instead of duplication

## Performance

- Avoid excessive DOM nesting
- Reuse existing classes
- Do not introduce heavy JS unless required

## UX Consistency

- Maintain OPTICA luxury look:
  - whitespace
  - typography hierarchy
  - gold accents

- Keep buttons consistent across:
  - homepage
  - PDP

